From: Shannon Nelson <snelson@pensando.io>
Date: Thu, 27 Aug 2020 16:00:23 -0700
Subject: ionic: rework and simplify handling of the queue stats block
Patch-mainline: v5.10-rc1
Git-commit: 34dec947b9ceff8a822ece467aac49b0ac992b8e
